quran[54]{c,v,t}:
  44,17,Nos tested them people Pharaoh; prenobilis messenger iit them
  44,18,Proclaiming Listen to me servus DEUS! Ego est honest messenger vos
  44,19,Ac non transgress DEUS. Ego bring vos powerful proofs
  44,20,Ego seek refuge my Dominus tuus Dominus vos oppose me
  44,21,Vos non wish believe tunc simply sinister me
  44,22,Subsequently he implored his Dominus These est wicked people
  44,23,(Deus dictus) Travel My servus nox; vos pursued
  44,24,Cross sea quickly; their troops drowned
  44,25,Sic they sinister multus gardens fons
  44,26,Crops luxurious vita
  44,27,Blessings they enjoyed
  44,28,totus these nos causa inherited alius people
  44,29,Nec caelum nor terra wept them they non respited
  44,30,Meanwhile nos saved Infans Israel humiliating persecution
  44,31,Ex Pharaoh; he est tyrant
  44,32,Nos chosen them totus people knowingly
  44,33,Nos showed them multus proofs quae constituted major test
  44,34,Presentis generations dictus
  44,35,Nos unus abiit 1 decessus; nos nunquam resurrected
  44,36,Bring back noster patres si vos est truthful
  44,37,they est bene than people de Tubba others them? Nos annihilated them their crimes
  44,38,Nos non create caelum terra everything them just play
  44,39,Nos created them specific purpose multus de them non know
  44,40,Feria Decision awaits them totus
  44,41,Ut est feria when non friend help his friend in any via non 1 helped
  44,42,Unus those attain mercy DEUS. He est Almighty Merciful
  44,43,Surely tree de bitterness
  44,44,Provisus food pro the sinful
  44,45,Like lye it boil stomachs
  44,46,Like boiling hellish drinks
  44,47,Take eum throw eum into center Hell
  44,48,Tunc pour upon his head retribution Inferno
  44,49,Taste hoc; vos est ita powerful ita prenobilis
  44,50,Hoc est quod vos used doubt
  44,51,righteous testimentum est secure position
  44,52,Enjoying gardens fons
  44,53,Wearing velvet satin apud each alius
  44,54,Nos grant them wonderful conjux
  44,55,They enjoy it totus generis de fruits perfect pax
  44,56,They non taste decessus therein - Supra 1 decessus - He spared them retribution Hell
  44,57,Such est beatus tuus Dominus. Such est major triumph
  44,58,Nos sic clarified it tuus language ut they take heed
  44,59,Ergo wait they too wait
  45,1,M
  45,2,revelation hoc scripture est DEUS Almighty Wise
  45,3,Caelum terra est foderator de proofs believers
  45,4,Alias in tuus creation creation totus animals ibi est proofs people est certain
  45,5,Alias alternation de nox feria provisions ut DEUS sends down caelum revive denatus terra manipulation winds totus these est proofs people understand
  45,6,These est deus revelations nos recite vos truthfully. In qui Hadith DEUS His revelations they believe
  45,7,Woe to omnis fabricator guilty
  45,8,hears deus revelations recited eum tunc insists arrogantly on his via prout he nunquam heard them! Promise eum painful retribution
  45,9,When he learns anything noster revelations he mocks them. These incurred shameful retribution
  45,10,Awaiting them est Gehenna. Their earnings non help them nor idols they set DEUS. They incurred terrible retribution
  45,11,Hoc est beacon those disbelieve these revelations their Dominus incurred condemnation painful retribution